Forget about Grandma.

00:23:57.339 --> 00:23:58.700
You're never allowed to see her again.

00:23:58.799 --> 00:23:59.480
Why?

00:23:59.480 --> 00:24:02.440
I told Grandma everything you taught me to say.

00:24:02.759 --> 00:24:04.420
It's useless to say anything now.

00:24:04.420 --> 00:24:06.680
Our area isn't being relocated anymore.

00:24:10.099 --> 00:24:10.619
Hello?

00:24:11.140 --> 00:24:11.700
It's me.

00:24:14.500 --> 00:24:15.660
I want to go back!

00:24:15.660 --> 00:24:16.299
Shh!

00:24:16.579 --> 00:24:17.660
Don't make a sound.

00:24:17.779 --> 00:24:18.859
If you upset your mom,

00:24:18.859 --> 00:24:20.099
I'll get in trouble too.

00:24:21.880 --> 00:24:23.119
For real?

00:24:25.279 --> 00:24:27.099
Is there a confirmation?

00:24:27.440 --> 00:24:29.140
You can't jerk people around like this.

00:24:31.059 --> 00:24:31.619
Okay.

00:24:31.619 --> 00:24:32.519
Got it.

00:24:36.720 --> 00:24:37.579
Stop the car.

00:24:37.900 --> 00:24:39.519
Turn around. Back to the nursing home.

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:40.980
What are you doing?

00:24:41.940 --> 00:24:43.440
Hurry, take this stuff...

00:24:43.500 --> 00:24:44.539
and Doudou...

00:24:44.579 --> 00:24:45.819
and send them back to your mom.

00:24:47.259 --> 00:24:49.420
Why do you change your mind every second?

00:24:49.500 --> 00:24:50.880
What is this nonsense?

00:24:51.619 --> 00:24:53.019
Can you blame me?

00:24:53.119 --> 00:24:55.339
My best friend just called again.

00:24:56.059 --> 00:24:57.400
Confirmed news.

00:24:57.799 --> 00:24:58.680
Our neighborhood...

00:24:58.880 --> 00:25:00.619
is being relocated again.

00:25:01.220 --> 00:25:01.920
Really?